LeetPrep is a handy interview preparation tool for developers. It contains the most commonly used resources to prepare for tech interviews. 


LeetPrep Features
- Programming Languages Documentation (Python, Java)
    - References to built-in functions and data structures with examples.
- Big O complexity tables and charts  for Data Structures & Sorting
- Common problem-solving techniques (Leetcode Patterns)
- Quick access to a curated list of popular interview questions (Blind 75)


Why I built LeetPrep?
I built LeetPrep to help me prepare for technical interviews. 

Having easy access to a curated set of resources was very useful while doing leetcode problems or simply studying for interviews. 

It is fast and convenient to look up how a function is used or the Big O of a specific data structure. It is always available on your browser with a click.


Contributing
LeetPrep is a fully open-source project and contributions are welcome to improve the extension. Visit our GitHub to learn more -> https://github.com/bleuscor/LeetPrep
